 CRobotContainerThis class is where the bulk of the robot should be declared. Since Command-based is a "declarative" paradigm, very little robot logic should actually be handled in the Robot periodic methods (other than the scheduler calls). Instead, the structure of the robot (including subsystems, commands, and button mappings) should be declared here
